'''Aksil''' ({{Tifinaɣ|ⴰⴽⵙⵉⵍ}} , s [[Talatint|tlatint]]: ''Caecilius'', gan as w-aεrabn ɣ idlisn nnsn : ''كسيلة'' ) iga yan ugllid amaziɣ d amɣar n taqbilt n [[Awraba]], Illul ɣ tiɣrmt n Txncelt ɣ tmazirt n [[Dzayr|Dzayer]], yenbeḍ yat tgeldit tamaziɣt yellan ɣ [[Tunes]] d utaram n [[Dzayr|Dzayer]]. Yezga-d wakal nnes zɣ [[Wahran]] d [[Tlemsan]] ɣ utaram ar tiɣremt n [[Qayrawan]] ɣ ugmuḍ. Ittuyssan baḥra ɣ tizi n ukccum n waεrabn s [[Tafriqt n ugafa]] niɣd [[Tamzɣa|Tamazɣa]]. Ig s tajdt [[Tamasiḥit|tamasiḥiyt]] lli rad ifl bac ad ikcm s [[Lislam]]. Mac rad immiqqir d yan uxatar n w-aεrabn [[Ɛuqba Bnu Nafiε]] lli rad t isimẓi izzugz ɣ watig nns lgddam n ayt dars d ixatarn yaḍn n tmazirt nns, mayad rad isgerwl tannayt nns f waεrabn ig awttas lli rad ittḥi s [[Lislam]]. Rad ilmma yaf taɣarast s tagrawla f kullu maygan [[Taεrabt|aεrab]] wala amusml. Rad yurri s [[Qayrawan]] ikkist i w-aεrabn, mac rad immt ɣ tasbaytad lgddam n Umayyadn.
